WEBVTT

00:02:59.625 --> 00:03:03.101
One hundred one years from now.

00:03:03.125 --> 00:03:05.268
Looking beyond the wage gap,

00:03:05.292 --> 00:03:08.309
women are still
underrepresented in leadership,

00:03:08.333 --> 00:03:11.184
receive less access to senior leaders

00:03:11.208 --> 00:03:13.518
and are leaving
the fastest-growing sectors,

00:03:13.542 --> 00:03:14.851
such as tech,

00:03:14.875 --> 00:03:18.934
at 45 percent higher rates than men,

00:03:18.958 --> 00:03:23.042
citing culture as the primary reason.

00:03:23.875 --> 00:03:27.018
So what have we been doing
to address gender inequality?

00:03:27.042 --> 00:03:29.143
Why isn't it working?

00:03:29.167 --> 00:03:31.809
Many businesses think
they're addressing the problem,